_sText:
After slaving over these things for about a week of time, I've finally decided to upload these,  I decided to make some cabin Prefabs for people to use in their outdoor maps and such, if anyone uses these just put me in as a cabin maker somewhere.

******IMPORTANT INFORMATION*******
The large and medium cabins may have some features missings, these are func_breakable_surfs, to fix this just make the windows a func_breakable_surf, also in the large cabin the two hatches to the roof and from the lower area are supposed to be sliding doors, so implement those aswell, 
***************************************

HAVE FUN!
